{"tid":1720652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實二噁英才是核彈","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:19:51.000Z","uid":259279,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e434ed9b12b64e1317dbcf21ed1d6288c1275d72","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"想想中環放了那麼多枚Tg，會有多少殘餘物。班中環精英以為無野，但其實已經殘餘體內、帶返屋企。所以應該要主力煲大二噁英，因為這是<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府對全港市民用生化武器</span></span></span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天的立場哥哥，就是明天的每一位香港市民</span></span>。"},{"pid":"be471c14e116bbea7f7ffed223aa1d076ee38e81","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"75d1661a734986b334a8770a42d19389029608eb","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"9b06cca02a52ca875ee766f079b0afec5b2c2e50","tid":1720652,"uid":295217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3173feced2c8f4dd7284a2fd9fffc9fec7b06402","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"727c1919f315966a4d5ba3e6fc4cb609f553df39","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"aa3f252806cf2b1760716702b935def99dc4dc79","tid":1720652,"uid":259279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"a1eef7c123684218597c13d300341a7298d0a41b","tid":1720652,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"dd0a5ef0da3e5697493f993e328a948f7f28b36b","tid":1720652,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12: